# templates/understand-anything.gitattributes
#
# Apply these lines to the consuming repo's root `.gitattributes` (append if the
# file exists, create if it does not). They commit the Understand-Anything artifact
# (Point #1) while suppressing its diff in PRs and excluding it from language stats.
#
# Source of truth: workflows/repo-init.md §1 and templates/understand-anything-action.yml.

.understand-anything/knowledge-graph.json binary -diff linguist-generated
.understand-anything/**             linguist-generated

# Leave `.understand-anything/config.json` and any plugin manifests
# (`.claude-plugin`, `.cursor-plugin`, `.copilot-plugin`) committed as plain text —
# those are small, human-curated and SHOULD diff normally.
